room_title: Escape room "King Neptune's Trident" by Escape Room Virginia Beach in Virginia Beach

room_description: A war is raging and King Neptune's Trident has been taken! You and your soldiers have been summoned to capture his trident from an underwater castle. Retrieve the trident, or the protection of our Virginia Beach shore, and the fate of the world, will be changed forever...
